text: Chassal-Molinges is a commune in the Jura department in Bourgogne-Franche- Comté in eastern France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Molinges (the seat) and Chassal.Arrêté préfectoral 11 December 2018 == See also == * Communes of the Jura department == References == * INSEE commune file Category:Communes of Jura (department) Category:Populated places established in 2019
